!! Quick summarize

Zero-config example. No context template, no prompt template — uses the built-in default (renders source tiddler text as plain text). Result displayed only.

''Settings covered:'' action mode, default behavior (no template), `output-mode: text`, `output-target: display`

```
<$button>
  Summarize this
  <$llm-action
    tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
    prompt="Summarize the most important points in 3 bullet points."
  />
</$button>
```

